      <para id="id10112553"/>
      <para id="id10112558">Đặt T = 
<m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mrow><m:mi>G</m:mi><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mi>C</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>S</m:mi><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mi>α</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ {  {G "." C}  over  {S "." α} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> là hằng số thời gian phát nóng.</para>
      <para id="id10112633"><m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mstyle fontsize="12pt"><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>S</m:mi><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mi>α</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:mstyle><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{ {  {P}  over  {S "." α} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math>= ôđ : độ chênh nhiệt ổn định. Ta có:</para>
      <para id="id10112716"> = ôđ ( 1-
